{"tid":1131764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癡撚線左癌AOC: 合法定非法入境冇所謂，要求取消移民及海關執法局！！","createTime":"2019-04-30T01:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T10:52:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"38f7ef0dc93ca39a8fd6eadc88038d78c05cf1e0","tid":1131764,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:03:48.000Z","msg":"Ocasio-Cortez: 'I Don't Care If You're Documented Or Undocumented'<br />\n<br />\nDemocratic Socialist Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez has gone full Soros, telling an audience at a Saturday town hall event in New York that <strong>America's immigration system is &quot;completely unjust,&quot; and that a person's immigration status doesn't matter to her. </strong><br />\n<br />\nThe New York Rep. also said that President Trump is &quot;creating&quot; populations of illegal immigrants by &quot;grinding all of the agencies to a halt that process the legal forms of immigration,&quot; which she says is &quot;forcing people into the shadows.&quot; <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;First of all I believe in human rights,&quot; AOC continued. &quot;I don&rsquo;t care if you&rsquo;re documented or you&rsquo;re undocumented.&quot;</span></strong>⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<strong>AOC has also <span style=\"color: red;\">repeatedly called for the abolishment of US Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE</span>), claiming the agency is racist and has &quot;systematically violated human rights.&quot; </strong><br />\n<br />\n&quot;The president should not be asking for more money to an agency that has systematically violated human rights. The president should be really defending why we are funding such an agency at all because right now what we are seeing is death,&quot; she told MSNBC's Rachel Maddow in January, adding: &quot;The president should be really defending why we are funding such an agency at all. Right now, what we are seeing is death. Right now, what we are seeing is the violation of human rights.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zerohedge.com/news/2019-04-29/ocasio-cortez-i-dont-care-if-youre-documented-or-undocumented\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerohedge.com%2Fnews%2F2019-04-29%2Focasio-cortez-i-dont-care-if-youre-documented-or-undocumented&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=d0bab69f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zerohedge.com/news/2019-04-29/ocasio-cortez-i-dont-care-if-youre-documented-or-undocumented</a>"},{"pid":"dfd4253756ccc95bbabdc5934d4bde504f12e6da","tid":1131764,"uid":215225,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"民主黨=左癌青山"},{"pid":"e641e07827e5edf54343422b9a722e36e34c4793","tid":1131764,"uid":81113,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"不如我哋都去果邊移民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30d78c50d35d12aa9fb55db631c7b9318769c34","tid":1131764,"uid":16846,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"送佢去中東俾人鞭打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55eaf1853d372fb3e8317dfa33c688149a45dc7d","tid":1131764,"uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"富足得太耐就會呢d反智傻佬"},{"pid":"d51934b040bf5b36c49082f49a41e8613fb5291b","tid":1131764,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"咁要分國家黎做乜"},{"pid":"c709d44bda54486ffdd61e74151213721554db5d","tid":1131764,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"支持aoc個d左膠真係讀書讀壞腦"},{"pid":"21c5cd31876b1282195c71ff8f4e2f4120cc11a5","tid":1131764,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c709d44bda54486ffdd61e74151213721554db5d","tid":1131764,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"支持aoc個d左膠